		<div class="comment-body"><p>I disagree with you on the cordless drills, I use drills everyday and I used to use Dewalt but I switched to Porter Cable, the 12v Porter Cable out preforms the 18v Dewalt by a long shot, the lithium ion batteries last for days unlike the Dewalt witch last only hours</p>
